signed four cooperation agreements following a friendship and
cooperation pact which was inked by the two countries Monday.
</P>
<P>
The cooperation pacts were signed during a meeting between
Greek Foreign Undersecretary Yannos Kranidiotis and visiting
Georgian Foreign Minister Irakli Menagarishvili.
</P>
