<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, September 16 (Xinhua) -- The Ethiopian Road
Authority today announced that a total of 647 kms of road will be
constructed this budget year beginning from last July in various
parts of the country.
</P>
<P>
Speaking at a meeting in the capital, General Manager of the
authority Tesfa-Michael Nahusenay said 485 kms will be built by
the authority itself and the remaining by contractors.
</P>
