according to the general manager, six bridges and two
maintenance camps will also be constructed during the year.
</P>
<P>
Nahusenay said that the authority has earmarked over 181.7
million Birr (about 26.7 million U.S.Dollars) for the road
construction it undertakes, adding that more than 536.2 million
Birr (about 78.8 million U..S Dollars) has been allocated for
the road to be constructed by contractors.
</P>
<P>
The Ethiopian Road Authority has planned to construct 1,077
kms of road in the coming five years in various parts of the
country. 
