Iranians by some unidentified gunmen was "a move to defame
Pakistan". Earlier, local police disclosed that five persons
including three Iranian Air Force trainees were killed and two
seriously injured in Rawalpindi, the sister city of the Pakistani
capital, by three unidentified gunmen. (Pakistan-Shooting)
</P>
