Li Yuning, deputy director of the company's enterprise
management department, said: "Every change has resulted from the
guidance of Deng Xiaoping Theory, and it is the will of the whole
Party and the whole people that Jiang has proposed adherence to
the Deng Xiaoping Theory as the guiding principle of the Party."
</P>
<P>
