<HEADLINE> Olympics-Bullet train unveiled for Winter Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, September 17 (Xinhua) -- An Olympics bullet train was
publicly unveiled on Wednesday, making the run 90 minutes faster
between Tokyo and Nagano, the site of the 1998 Winter Games.
</P>
<P>
