promotional buildup for the February 7-22 Winter Games.
</P>
<P>
The 84 billion yen (about 700 million U.S. dollars) bullet
train can carry 630 passengers at a speed of 260 kilometers an
hour, said Ryuichi Furuta, a spokesman for JR East Railways, which
will operate the line. Endtiem

