<HEADLINE> Collection of Studies on Deng Xiaoping Theory Published </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 17 (Xinhua) -- "A Collection of Studies on
Deng Xiaoping Theory" was recently released by the Publishing
House under the Central Party School, as part of the effort to
promote the study and research on Deng nationwide.
</P>
<P>
The collection, which includes over 2,000 articles and a total
of 12 million words, is a systematic review of the achievements
made in research and study on Deng's speeches in his well-known
southern tour in 1992 and the progress of Deng Xiaoping Theory
since then.
</P>
<P>
