<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 17 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
September 18 issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at
17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 8 degrees c., max. 23 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 5 degrees c., max. 18 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 10 degrees c., max. 23 degrees c., cloudy to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 13 degrees c., max. 19 degrees c., drizzle to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 17 degrees c., max. 22 degrees c., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
