<HEADLINE> Venezuelan Party Congratulates CPC on Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 17 (Xinhua) -- The Christian Socialist Party
(CSP) of Venezuela has sent a congratulatory message to the
Communist Party of China (CPC) on its 15th National Congress.
</P>
<P>
In the telegram to CPC Central Committee General Secretary
Jiang Zemin, CSP National President Luis Herrera Campins and
General Secretary Donald Ramirez Molina said they warmly
congratulate the Communist Party of China on its 15th National
Congress.
</P>
<P>
The friendly and long-standing relationship of mutual benefit
between the two parties brings the two peoples closer and deepens
their mutual understanding, they said.
</P>
<P>
They wished the congress a great success and resolutions from
it show the prospect of progress, dignity and justice of the
Chinese people.
</P>
<P>
The new historical period that the congress has opened will
become a phase for all the Chinese people to make progress in
material and spirit.
</P>
<P>
China, which will continue its modern construction and
opening-up process, is expected to play ever more important roles
in the world, they predicted. 
</P>
</TEXT>
