<HEADLINE> Southwest China Investment And Trade Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, September 17 (Xinhua) -- An investment and trade fair
has been scheduled for Chengdu, capital of southwest China's
Sichuan province, from September 23 to 27.
</P>
<P>
The fair is being sponsored by Yunnan, Guizhou, and Sichuan
provinces, the Guangxi Zhuang and Tibet Autonomous regions, and
Chongqing, which was changed last March from the largest city in
southwest China to a municipality directly under the central
government, the State Council.
