<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, September 16 (Xinhua) -- Mark Johnson of the United
States retained his IBF flyweight title by winning a unanimous
decision over Angel Almena of Puerto Rico in Tennessee Tuesday
night.
</P>
