expenditure was 1,450 rupees (about 41 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
During the hearing on Tuesday, the CBI told the court that
Kesri's son, Amarnath Kesri, had also amassed disproportionate
assets over two million rupees (about 57,000 dollars).  
