<HEADLINE> Colombia Cuts Budget on Political Campaigns </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTA FE DE BOGOTA, September 16 (Xinhua) -- Colombia's
National Electoral Committee has decided to reduce the budget for
parliamentary elections scheduled for March 8, 1998.
</P>
