dominance from the onset and maintained their momentum till the
final whistle, the coach said.
</P>
<P>
On Wednesday, China will play Saudi Arabia and the Chinese
coach was confident of beating the hosts although both sides have
secured their semifinal berths.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese are determined to enter the semifinals as group
winners because they enjoyed height advantage with better defense
and clever tactics, the coach said.
</P>
<P>
