<HEADLINE> 55 Homicides in Sao Paulo Over Weekend </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, September 16 (Xinhua) -- Sao Paulo witnessed
last weekend 55 homicides in its streets, from 20:00 Friday to
8:00 Monday.
</P>
<P>
The number of murders committed over the weekend is the highest
to take place since 57 assassinations occured between February 28
and March 3, secretary of Public Safety in Sao Paulo, Jose Alfonso
Da Silva, told reporters today.
</P>
<P>
Sao Paulo is a city with an extremely high crime rate, with
nearly 7,000 homicides reported last year. 
